    Log List    ${logs}
    :FOR    ${log}    IN    @{logs}
    \    ${data}=    OperatingSystem.Get File    ${RESULTS_FOLDER}/${log}
    \    Should Not Contain    ${data}    exited: agent (exit status
    \    Should Not Contain    ${data}    exited: vpp (exit status
